
<div class="banner">
  <div class="banner-content">
    <h1>Fullstack Web <br> Developer</h1>
    <p>I build bespoke websites for individuals and small to medium businesses</p>
    <div class="button_wrapper">
        <a href="<%= projects_path %>" class="project_button" target="_blank">View my Work</a>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding  clearfix">
  <div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <hr>
    <p>I am a fullstack Ruby on Rails developer and consultant living in London.</p>
    <p>I can help you showcase your portfolio and skillset in the best possible manner, with an approach tailored to your achievements, and beautifully present your blog in a way that aligns with your core values and aims. I  build websites and web applications which expand to match the growth rate of your business, to provide both you and your clients an enjoyable, effortless and seamless user experience.</a></p>
    <p>As a former corporate investigator and strategic communications specialist, I can also provide advice on business strategy, and on how you can best reach your target audiences.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
    <h2>Things I've Written</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime('%e %B %Y') %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="col-3 homepage_content">
    <h2>Things I've Built</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to project.title, project %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime('%e %B %Y') %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
